"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The US president says the war with Iran will be over quickly, but Washington hasn't achieved enough yet. Many expect the 56-year-old leader, who has mostly stayed out of the spotlight, to continue his father's strict policies. There is concern for a team after a critic called them traitors for not saluting during the Iranian anthem. India says Tehran asked for permission to dock three ships on the day the US and Israel started a war on Iran.\",            \"english_title\": \"US-Iran War\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de EE.UU. dice que la guerra con Ir\u00e1n terminar\u00e1 r\u00e1pido, pero Washington no ha logrado mucho a\u00fan. Muchos esperan que el l\u00edder de 56 a\u00f1os, que ha estado fuera del foco, siga las pol\u00edticas estrictas de su padre. Hay preocupaci\u00f3n por un equipo despu\u00e9s de que un cr\u00edtico los llam\u00f3 traidores por no saludar durante el himno iran\u00ed. India dice que Teher\u00e1n pidi\u00f3 permiso para atracar tres barcos el d\u00eda que EE.UU. e Israel empezaron una guerra con Ir\u00e1n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Guerra EE.UU.-Ir\u00e1n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Finance ministers and the International Energy Agency discussed ways to stabilize oil prices, which have gone over $100. Training will include everything from traditional skills to drone control and cyberwarfare techniques and countermeasures.\",            \"english_title\": \"Oil Prices and Training\",            \"translated_version\": \"Ministros de finanzas y la Agencia Internacional de Energ\u00eda hablaron sobre c\u00f3mo estabilizar los precios del petr\u00f3leo, que han pasado de $100. El entrenamiento incluir\u00e1 desde habilidades tradicionales hasta control de drones y t\u00e9cnicas de ciber-guerra y contraataques.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Precios del petr\u00f3leo y entrenamiento\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Naveed Akram is trying to stop the media from publishing details about his mother, sister, and brother.\",            \"english_title\": \"Privacy Concerns\",            \"translated_version\": \"Naveed Akram est\u00e1 tratando de detener a los medios de publicar detalles sobre su madre, hermana y hermano.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Preocupaci\u00f3n por privacidad\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The Liberal government in Canada currently has 169 seats in parliament, just three short of a majority.\",            \"english_title\": \"Canadian Parliament\",            \"translated_version\": \"El gobierno liberal en Canad\u00e1 tiene actualmente 169 asientos en el parlamento, solo tres menos de una mayor\u00eda.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Parlamento canadiense\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Norwegian police say their investigation shows that Sunday's explosion was caused by an improvised device.\",            \"english_title\": \"Norway Explosion\",            \"translated_version\": \"La polic\u00eda noruega dice que su investigaci\u00f3n muestra que la explosi\u00f3n del domingo fue causada por un dispositivo improvisado.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Explosi\u00f3n en Noruega\"        }    ]}"